			"value": "<div class=\"repitem\" data-reprowid=\"-LIZcmPoSW6ZHJWcW0Gc\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;position:relative\"><div class=\"trait\" style=\"box-sizing:content-box;position:relative\"><div class=\"display\" style=\"box-sizing:content-box;margin-bottom:2px\"><p><span class=\"description\" style=\"box-sizing:content-box;text-align:left !important;display:block;font-size:13px;line-height:13px;width:385px;font-weight:normal;margin-top:0px;white-space:pre-line;color:var(--dark-secondarytext)\">The [[lookup @name lowercase]] are vestiges of a greater entity. This entity can communicate through them if the [[lookup @name lowercase]] touches the person the entity wants to talk to. The [[lookup @name lowercase]] can communicate telepathically in any language listed on this drone. </span></p><br><p><span class=\"description\" style=\"box-sizing:content-box;text-align:left !important;display:block;font-size:13px;line-height:13px;width:385px;font-weight:normal;margin-top:0px;white-space:pre-line;color:var(--dark-secondarytext)\">The malakai are mentally connected by either this entity or a local commander, such as Emrys or Lorkul. They know the location of all other malakai controlled by the same commander, and share all their senses. </span></p></div></div></div>",
